job.title: PGCIL Recruitment Notification 2021 – Apply Online for 35 Diploma Trainee vacancies in Uttar Pradesh
job.body:
Total vacancies:35

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Diploma Trainee

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Engineers and diploma holders have been published by Power Grid Corporation of India Limited for Diploma Trainee vacancies. If you are searching for a government job in Uttar Pradesh, Uttarakhand, Rajasthan, Haryana & Delhi then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Diploma Trainee, from 24.05.2021, and till 15.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for GEN/OBC candidates is only Rs. 300/-.
  • No application for SC/ST/PwD

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for Diploma Trainee in PGCIL, your Diploma, B.E, B.Tech must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 24.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 15.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 27  years old. 

PGCIL Diploma Trainee Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 25000 –117500.

How to apply for PGCIL Recruitment Notification 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Diploma Trainee. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of PGCIL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by PGCIL.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
